sense.def:
Kadar en dogodek ali obdobje
precedes another
, se zgodi pred drugim.

seg.quote: ...the drop in temperature that precedes a heavy thunderstorm.
The children's dinner was preceded by games.
...the activities we discussed in the preceding chapter.

sense.def:
To precede someone somewhere
pomeni iti pred nekom nekam.

seg.quote: She preceded him across the hallway.
We were preceded by a huge man called Teddy Brown.
